{"title":"git忽略已add文件的变动","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:18.982Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/git忽略已add文件的变动","updated":"2023-07-28T09:21:30.222Z","content":"<p>1、在目录下执行git命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git update-index --assume-unchanged $&#123;要忽略的文件&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、在gitignore文件中配置待忽略的文件</p>\n<p>恢复文件的上传</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git update-index --no-assume-unchanged $&#123;要恢复的文件&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Hadoop伪分布式安装","link":"2023/07/28/Hadoop伪分布式安装"},"next":{"title":"java后端配置跨域不生效、无效","link":"2023/07/28/java后端配置跨域不生效、无效"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/git忽略已add文件的变动/","reading_time":"56 字约 1 分钟"}